text: Neohebestola apicalis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaire and Germain in 1859. It is known from Chile.BioLib.cz - Neohebestola apicalis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Forsteriini Category:Beetles described in 1859
